Program: Last Word
Title: Sally Ride, Omar Suleiman, Rajesh Khanna, Jane Leighton and Jim Drake
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b01l1g62
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Jul 2012
Matthew Bannister on Sally Ride - who overcame sexism to become America's first woman astronaut. Omar Suleiman - head of Egypt's General Intelligence Service and right hand man to President Mubarak Bollywood superstar Rajesh Khanna, in his prime beloved by millions of swooning female fans Jane Leighton, the TV journalist who campaigned for the underdog And Jim Drake, the engineer who designed the modern windsurfer. Producer Neil McCarthy. Show less